an Broadcasting Company|ABC]]/[[DuMont Television Network|DuMont]] - Atlantic City (12/21/1952-5/17/1954)\n*Channel 48: [[WKBS-TV (Philadelphia)|WKBS-TV]] - Ind. - Burlington/Philadelphia (9/1/1965-8/29/1983)\n*Channel 58: [[WRTV (Asbury Park)|WRTV]] - [[Asbury Park, New Jersey|Asbury Park]] (12/14/1953-4/1/1955)\n*Channel 66: [[WNYJ-TV]] - ETV - [[West Milford, New Jersey|West Milford]]/New York (3/1/1996-10/25/2017)\n\n==[[Low-power broadcasting|LPTV]] stations==\n*Channel 7: [[WMGM-LP]] - Ind. - Atlantic City, etc.\n*Channel 8 (RF channel 27): [[WPSJ-CD]] - [[Azteca Am\u00e9rica]] - Hammonton\n*Channel 15 (RF channel 10): [[WSJT-LD]] - Atlantic City, 15.2 [[GEB_America|GEBTV]], 15.3 [[Faith_TV|FaithTV]], 15.4 [[Gospel_Broadcasting_Network|GBNTV]], 15.5 [[BVOTV]], 15.6 [[WeatherNation_TV|Weather]], 15.7 [[]], 15.8 [[]]\n*Channel 23 (RF channel 22): [[WDVB-CD]] - ([[Hillsong Channel|Hillsong]]/[[Smile (TV network)|Smile]]) - Edison\n*Channel 25 (RF channel 22): [[WPHY-CD]] - ([[Sonlife Broadcasting Network]]) - Trenton\n*Channel 27 (RF channel 20): [[W20EF-D]] - ([[Jewelry TV]]) - Teaneck \n*Channel 34 (RF channel 4): [[WPXO-LD]] - ([[Am\u00e9rica TeV\u00e9]]) - East Orange\n*Channel 34 (RF channel 26): [[WQAV-CD]] - ([[Jewelry TV]]) - Glassboro\n*Channel 41 (RF channel 16): [[WDUM-LD]] - ([[Home Shopping Network|HSN]]) - Springville\n*Channel 45: [[W45CP-D]] - ([[Daystar (TV network)|Daystar]]) - Atlantic City\n*Channel 48 (RF channel 48): [[W48DP-D]] - ([[Cornerstone Television|CTVN]]/GCN/CNL/ABN) - Atlantic City\n\n==[[Broadcast translator|Translators]]==\n*Channel 58 (RF channel 23): [[W23EX-D]] - [[NJTV]] repeater - Sussex\n*Channel 58 (RF channel 27): [[W43CH-D]] - [[NJTV]] repeater - Belvidere\n*Channel 58 (RF channel 29): [[W29EV-D]] - [[NJTV]] repeater - Hackettstown\n\n==See also==\n*[[The Comcast Network]]\n*[[NBC Sports Philadelphia]]\n*[[MSG (TV  channel)]]\n*[[MSG Plus]]\n*[[SportsNet New York]]\n*[[YES Network]]\n* [[List of Spanish-language televisi